message: I’m Not For Sale is an organization dedicated to raising awareness for sex trafficking in the state of Nebraska. These students want to shine light on a dark issue by advocating for those who are trapped in modern-day slavery.

data.description: As human trafficking becomes more prevalent around the world and Nebraska, a group of four University of Nebraska–Lincoln students felt the need to take a stand and help spread awareness
data.title: Four UNL students raise awareness for sex trafficking in Nebraska
